{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My husband has a little sister who lives now in Israel, a girl of 10 years, she was with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very difficult, a small place, and they live all together, living with the scraps, with the very small things which was going out-- going on outside.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, living with the hope that they will survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hope was constantly, constantly with the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I wonder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wonder how-- his mother was not a healthy woman-- how they were going on with life in this small hiding place having hope that they will survive.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they did survive, they did survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His mother knew that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The parents knew that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the people where they were hiding, they didn't know that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very-- it was on a small cemetery, a Greek Orthodox cemetery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was one small room, as I recall, where they were living, the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a small kitchen, so small.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in this kitchen they were living, four people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How they were able to sleep I don't know, probably staying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they, somehow they slept there, they kept Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't want to eat meat because it was not kosher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So even there, in their own way, they kept their Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they have-- it was a cemetery constantly close.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If somebody wants to get in, they were alarmed and they knew right away who was going to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As I recall, my husband used to help in some Orthodox-- Greek Orthodox died he used to walk and prepared the grave for the-- as a Pole.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is how I recall this hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband's name?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
